categories.name: starter
categories.desc: Dipping, rolling and sharing are what our starters and sides were made for. We make everything fresh in-house: homemade chilli paste, garlic, from our summer and spring rolls to our pork and lemongrass meatballs.

categories.name: pho
categories.desc: Phở, pronounced 'fuh' is the national dish of Vietnam. It's a fantastic steaming bowl of rice noodle soup served with a side plate of fresh herbs to add as you please.

categories.name: noodles
categories.desc: Vermicelli rice noodles with a lemongrass and chilli wok-fried topping. Served with fresh herbs, beansprouts, veggie spring roll and peanuts. Noodles served at room temp just like in Vietnam.

categories.name: drinks
categories.desc: Typical Vietnamese drinks, which can be consumed before, during and after meals. Let's add more flavor to your party.

categories.name: desserts
categories.desc: Our desserts range from rich ice creams and refreshing sorbets to our delicious and decadent chocolate truffle or fried banana fritters (which are gluten free and vegan!).
